subject: Basketball
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: A’dia Mathies scored 23 points and No. 10 Kentucky (9-0) beat No. 6 Duke, 72-65, in front of 14,508 fans at Rupp Arena, the largest home crowd for a women’s game in Wildcats history.
